  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd - \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I strongly condemn the attack on the protesters - Leader of Opposition",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "I strongly condemn the attack on the peaceful protestors by the present government which is a puppet of the Rajapaksas with their own violence. Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa has demanded immediate investigation against all those who ordered this barbaric attack.",
        "Using the usual brutality and violence of Rajapaksa's puppet government, the 'Shadow Rajapakse Government' has launched a cowardly and violent attack against the peaceful protestors of Kalimukha.",
        "Many local and foreign journalists and unarmed soldiers who came to cover it had to face that inhumane attack and this attack was brutal official violence in true sense.",
        "This inhumane attack has been carried out less than 24 hours after the inauguration of the new president. The new president has sought to convey that this is the nature of his future regime. We would like to remind him that beyond such atrocities strong governments have been overthrown by people power.",
        "The cowardly attack was carried out by the security forces in the early hours of the morning when the civilian militias were recapturing all the occupied areas. We don't know if the attack was carried out in hysteria against the Rajapaksa government trying to send it home.",
        "We always respect the democratic right of the people of the country to struggle and protest. We continue to stand for civilized protests instead of violence without damaging government property and public property.",
        "On the one hand, the way for the current president to come to power was the result of the struggle led by the people of this country, including the impeachment. Although this struggle did little to encourage him to become president, he gained power through it.",
        "It is sad that the President forgot about 12 hours after he was sworn in as President. Perhaps even anger that the protest led to the overthrow of Rajapaksa.",
        "The previous Rajapaksa government destroyed all chances of standing up as a civilized nation. That is what has started happening in the current 'Rajapaksha Shadow Government'. What is different is that Rajapaksa has turned into a radical fanaticism.",
        "Instead of understanding that the country has sunk into the abyss, acting only for its own power, this shadow government of Rajpaksha has brutally violated the fundamental right of people to protest and freedom and the freedom of the media.",
        "It has been informed that investigations should be conducted against all official and non-official officials who carried out the armed attack on the armed people, members and civilians and that all those who ordered this barbaric attack should be immediately investigated."
      ],
